nodes.bodyText:
I think we can solve it like this:
private Predicate<Class<?>> secureObjectValidator = (o) -> true;
private Predicate<ConfigAttribute> configAttributeValidator = (o) -> true;

public void setAccessDecisionManager(AccessDecisionManager accessDecisionManager) {
       this.secureObjectValidator = accessDecisionManager::supports;
       this.configAttributeValidator = accessDecisionManager::supports;
       this.authorizationManager = new AuthorizationManagerAdapter<>(accessDecisionManager,
		    (o) -> obtainSecurityMetadataSource().getAttributes(o));
}
What do you think, @jzheaux?

